assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最重要都係要學識擺位"},{"pid":"ae864c2c0e6b1e0f00873618bda6ab47aa05fb39","tid":145854,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"不同握法有唔同結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe948184c668a313bcb0c0ab1d44261e8d0c672","tid":145854,"uid":31819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣練大力？定係要練左肌肉先？</blockquote><br />\n睇你用喺邊方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果想喺拗手瓜個陣勁啲就練手腕先，後再練手臂。<br />\n如果唔係就算你手臂幾大力都好，手腕唔識去發力都係冇用"},{"pid":"e521f102be3258f8b01a42faac21182ef5b60e37","tid":145854,"uid":31819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學練過一排，但太專注右手搞到左右唔平衡，而家補救緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麒麟臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195fb637a795f060db11e7310ea7f7696db96669","tid":145854,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"好似係<br />\n<br />\n練手腕係搶先機<br />\n練手臂係防俾人壓低<br />\n練背肌係用黎壓低人"},{"pid":"004298c400eb4d2b9e0cd470ddddf6c0ba146ba7","tid":145854,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係<br />\n<br />\n練手腕係搶先機<br />\n練手臂係防俾人壓低<br />\n練背肌係用黎壓低人</blockquote><br />\n我一路都懷疑究竟搶先機係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見過好多人搶完都冇分別"}]}